title: Viewing history could include arrows.
pid: 019e51cb-898b-4e15-be30-e22369128d7d
body: |2-
  like the arrows [[id:5c2be847-0a45-4fa9-ae96-fc78f88fecad][Maria Paula draws in therapy sessions]].
  A simple history would just be (node, time) pairs.
  A better history would be (this node, maybe last node, time) pairs.
  When someone arrives at a node from search results, the maybe is None.
  This kind of data would let someone extract
  flow diagrams -- where they tend to go from where.
